BodyName: Subcommittee on Landmarks, Public Siting and Maritime Uses

Items.Title: Application no. 20095400 SCQ, a proposed site for a new, approximately 1,100 seat high school facility located at the northwest corner of 57th Avenue and 74th Street (Block 2803, Lot1) in Council District no. 30, Borough of Queens. Items.ActionText: This Land Use Application was Hearing Held by Committee
